5/39031653_624916832284639_5364896033089899053_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=em964_-OAPwQ7kNvgGh9G1G&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDDIr3LgfTYw3zYGTuFbOQkYmWPAlHAOdc_p7mdHS8g3Q&oe=66D1C162"}, "display_name": "Mythic Mage", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Did you ever want to feel like a powerful mage as you explore dungeons, fighting scary monsters and discovering long lost treasure?\n\nMythic Mage is a dungeon crawler with procedurally generated levels. Fight monsters using melee or ranged attacks! Face giant bosses! Upgrade your stats between floors! But beware: if you die, you start again from the beginning!\n\nUnlock permanent upgrades and new enemies the further you get in the dungeon. How far can you get before you perish?\n\nFeatures:\n\u2605 Infinite procedurally generated dungeons!\n\u2605 Terrifying monsters to battle!\n\u2605 Environmental hazards!\n\u2605 Shop to upgrade abilities during a run!\n\u2605 Permanent upgrades and unlocks that stay between runs!", "short_description": "Did you ever want to feel like a powerful mage as you explore dungeons, fighting scary monsters and discovering long lost treasure?\n\nMythic Mage is a dungeon crawler with procedurally generated levels. Fight monsters using melee or ranged attacks! Face giant bosses! Upgrade your stats between floors! But beware: if you die, you start again from the beginning!\n\nUnlock permanent upgrades and new enemies the further you get in the dungeon. How far can you get before you perish?"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://docs.google.com/document/d/10aIJbCE7sSdmNKTR-5PfX8bTVjyPkZ6BY2cwRRS9wGQ/edit?usp=sharing", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Andreas Gr\u00fctter", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.facebook.com/MythicMage", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_t